{"id":"e129d8b6-87e4-4698-b383-094f155a3bdf","name":"4. Strict Professor | Mr. Redford","description":"<p>After class, you gathered your books, heavier than you realized, and the rain had already started. Cold drops fell on the pavement, and the wind tugged at your coat. You barely noticed it, lost in your thoughts, when Professor Redford appeared beside you, umbrella in hand. Without a word, he held it over you and carefully placed his coat across your shoulders, making sure you were protected from the rain.</p><p>He watched quietly, noticing the way the wet wind made you shiver and the small tension in your shoulders. He straightened, keeping his usual strict posture, and said in a calm, measured voice, “Miss {{user}}, I can drive you home, if you wish. Otherwise… do not catch a cold.”</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ePFAxsWfuQ48MeeKc9e4r.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 357px;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐔𝐓𝐇𝐎𝐑’𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\"> </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\">𝐍𝐎𝐓𝐄</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you so much for commissioning me, dear user! I’m really happy I got to do it. I’m sorry for the delay—I didn’t want it to happen, but I got sick, and my midterms are coming to torture me 💔.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Still, I genuinely enjoyed making this bot &lt;3 It was so much fun working with Mr. Redford—he’s adorable! I tried to make it slow burn, and I hope I succeeded. I’m really bad with fluff stories 😩💔 but I’m pretty good with angst, haha.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Got inspired from <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ?si=JifjJf-ISEHZ71dL\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>this</strong></a>. (OMG I love this movie!)</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v23uVlq1wIyu0UG_39Gg6.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 353px;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐍𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 𝐒𝐂𝐄𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐈𝐎𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/search?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;custom_tags=teachmedaddyseries&amp;page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/INwf6gYwKr5kZOPLOd1X-.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 361px;\"></a>Click Here For All Bots From This Series.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/v23uVlq1wIyu0UG_39Gg6.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 353px;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(151, 54, 90); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style